Articles.Content:
Hey guys, I'm trying to get clouds and city lights with EVE but it's not working.

I downloaded the two zips from https://github.com/rbray89/EnvironmentalVisualEnhancements/releases/tag/Beta-3 , unzipped them and put contents in game_data, so that my game_data folder now contains Boulderco and EnvironmentalVisualEnhancements folders as well as squad. However I see no difference in game.

Kubuntu 16.10, 64bit client, ksp 1.2.2

The player.log is showing errors with eve but I'm not sure what to do with the info, maybe someone can help.
I've put it in a spoiler but it's huge (although the errors seem to be at the top), here's a link to the uploaded file if that's easier to work with (pastebin said it was too big): https://www.NoFile.io/f/Eg0bw4Ud7YP
